{"tid":1376524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四川綿陽傳爆炸 近20名中共官員受傷","createTime":"2019-07-28T10:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T03:32:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":138,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"fc66380080e6ec8fe9c74b6b0c988ebcce60520d","tid":1376524,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:53:22.000Z","msg":"中國四川省綿陽市警方公布，游仙區石馬鎮一處社區樓房26日發生爆炸，正在現場開會的近20名中共官員和一名嫌犯受傷；警方未交代嫌犯犯案動機，但當地多年來強拆事件不斷。<br />\n<br />\n中共人民日報引述綿陽市公安局游仙區分局消息說，游仙區一個在建社區26日中午發生爆炸案，石馬鎮政府幹部組織社區黨員幹部當時正在事發地的一樓開會，爆炸導致多人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n據表示，包含嫌犯在內的5人傷勢較重，另15人輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n網上照片顯示，現場出現多輛警車和救護車，而事發大樓掛著布條，寫上「游仙區石馬鎮七姓壩片區拆遷指揮部」字樣。<br />\n<br />\n綿陽市和游仙區兩級公安正在調查案件，但官方未交代犯案動機。<br />\n<br />\n美國自由亞洲電台報導，石馬鎮多年來不時傳出村民遭到毆打和房屋被強拆的事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7332/3955617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7332%2F3955617&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=034a1dbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7332/3955617</a>"},{"pid":"cb6f4948fe85ce4cb64964ab070fa55ef522d27c","tid":1376524,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65aed08e9eaf8478235bfc8dcedb01e608499b57","tid":1376524,"uid":290176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 星火燎原"},{"pid":"7c8aedbf00f1a8a1c61fe5de42ac55ded3ab838c","tid":1376524,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:55:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[728] 需要地方落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee96bf77878503df3234b8854